类的使用
com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.MadnessServlet

  • 使用MadnessServlet的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    com.chipsandwaycool.servlet  
    com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.game  
    com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.player  
    com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.team  

    • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet中MadnessServlet的使用

      com.chipsandwaycool.servlet中MadnessServlet的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  Home
      This is the home page for the March Madness Web site.
      class  Initialization
      This is the initializer servlet for the March Madness site.
      class  Instructions
      This servlet outputs a page of instructions detailing how this site works.
      class  Login
      The Login servlet processes the login form displayed on the home page, redirecting back to that page upon successful login or to display an authentication error.

    • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.game中MadnessServlet的使用

      com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.game中MadnessServlet的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  EditWinners
      The Edit Winners page is used to enter and modify the winners of any game for which both teams are known.
      class  EditWinnersAction
      This guy responds to the Edit Winners form by assigning the winners of games according to the user input and then asking the business object to "reconcile" the user's selections.

    • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.player中MadnessServlet的使用

      com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.player中MadnessServlet的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  EditPlayer
      This servlet allows for editing of new and existing players (that is, users of this Web site).
      class  EditPlayerAction
      Here's the action handler for the Edit Player form page.
      class  EmailPicks
      This servlet uses an emailer component to send a list of everyone's picks to everyone's email addresses.
      class  EmailScores
      This servlet uses the Emailer to send a list of everyone's current scores to everyone else.
      class  Picks
      This is the page where users can choose the twenty teams they think likeliest to win, arranging according to points values from 20 down to one point.
      class  PicksAction
      This servlet processes the form input submitted through the Picks page.
      class  PicksCSV
      This servlet outputs a CSV file (with the appropriate content-type header) containing a list of users on this site and the twenty teams they picked on the "Pick Teams" page.
      class  Scoreboard
      The Scoreboard is where each player (user) on this site is listed along with their scores for each round, total scores and highest potential scores, for comparison.

    • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.team中MadnessServlet的使用

      com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.team中MadnessServlet的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  EditTeams
      This page is used to modify the set of sixty-four teams in the tournament.
      class  EditTeamsAction
      This "action" servlet responds to the Edit Teams page, updating the names of all sixty-four teams when a site administrator has changed them.
